    "HOMEOPATHY": "The art of curing, founded on resemblances; the theory and itspractice that disease is cured (tuto, cito, et jucunde) by remedieswhich produce on a healthy person effects similar to the symptoms ofthe complaint under which the patient suffers, the remedies beingusually administered in minute doses. This system was founded by Dr.Samuel Hahnemann, and is opposed to allopathy, or heteropathy.[Written also homoepathy.]",
    "HOMER": "A carrier pigeon remarkable for its ability to return home froma distance.",
