    "HYGIEIST": "A hygienist.",
    "HYGIENE": "That department of sanitary science which treats of thepreservation of health, esp. of households and communities; a systemof principles or rules designated for the promotion of health.",
    "HYGIENIC": "Of or pertaining to health or hygiene; sanitary.",
